entry.value: SELECT (price) AS column0, (age) AS column1, (-(horsepower)) AS column2, (-(CASE WHEN color IN ('green', 'black') THEN 1 WHEN color IN ('brown', 'yellow', 'white', 'blue', 'silver') THEN 0 WHEN color IN ('red') THEN -1 END)) AS column3, (mileage) AS column4 FROM (SELECT * FROM car) as T
SELECT * FROM (SELECT * FROM car) AS T PREFERRING ((price LOWEST PRIOR TO age LOWEST) AND (horsepower HIGHEST PRIOR TO color LAYERED (('green', 'black'), OTHERS, ('red'))) AND mileage LOWEST)
